                    "type": "scenario",
                    "scenario": "A publisher notices high latency on their page load (3s+) purely due to ad tags. They are currently using client-side Header Bidding with 15 adapters.",
                    "question": "What is the most effective architectural change to reduce latency while maintaining demand pressure?",
